'''Galactic Alliance Intelligence officer'''{{'s}} were [[Officer/Legends|officers]] of the [[Galactic Alliance Intelligence Service]]. During the [[Second Imperial Civil War]], three of them accompanied [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Gar Stazi]] of the [[Galactic Alliance Remnant]] to [[The Wheel/Legends|The Wheel]] and served as [[Bodyguard/Legends|bodyguards]] while Stazi negotiated with [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Mingo Bovark]] of the [[Empire-in-exile]]. They engaged in a brief [[lightfight]] with the [[Imperial Knight]]s [[Antares Draco]] and [[Ganner Krieg]] after the negotiations were [[Skirmish on The Wheel|sabotaged]] by [[Agent/Legends|agents]] of [[Darth Krayt's Galactic Empire]].

==Behind the scenes==
On the cover of [[Legacy (2006) 10|''Legacy'' (2006) 10]], the Intelligence [[Officer/Legends|officers]] on The Wheel were incorrectly depicted as [[Color/Legends|blue]]-[[Armor/Legends|armor]]&ndash;wearing [[Trooper/Legends|troopers]] that would later be identified as [[Galactic Alliance Infantry Trooper]]s in the ''[[Legacy Era Campaign Guide]]''.

